Class CircleOfTrustDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.identity.cot.CircleOfTrustDescriptor

  • public class CircleOfTrustDescriptor
extends Object
    The COTDescriptor class is the representation of the circle of trust configuration.
